divs: Sighting Details i'm 66 years old male. i was riding in the back seat of a freinds car,with my wife,i was on the right side. i was looking at my wife to my left. and i seen out her window something i have never seen before. it was low flying maybe 3 hundred feet high.it was bright orange. i could see it maybe 4 seconds it was going stright. with a flat Trajectorey.it was going faster than anything i have ever seen.like a tracer bulit.way biger than a airplane. i called the kenosha news the next day they said they had several other reports of seeing this ufo. i seen this in 2007 i'm not realy sure of the date. there were 4 of us in the car i was the only one to see it,because i was the only one looking in that direction. about 2 seconds after i seen it, i said hey you guys [ i just seen a flying sauser.] larry valentine
Summary: i seen a ufo , nothing like i ever seen before
